summary: Converted Jarl Elisif into Cercei Lannister (Game of Thrones)
descriptionHtml:
UPDATED:
totally re-made. Now she\'s more similar.

DESCRIPTION:
Hi guys,
I\'ve converted Jarl Elisif into Cercei Lannister (Game of Thrones).
Yeah, I know...the hairstyle is not the same, but If you could find something more similar, just use NPC Editor and replace it.
;-)

INSTALL:
1. put content (meshes folder, ElisifTheFair.esp) into your data folder.
2. enjoy

REQUIRED:
- Apachii Hair 
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=10168
- Jarls New Clothes (if you want the same outfit as the preview)
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=2698

MY OTHER CONVERSIONS:
- Ulfric --> Eddard Stark
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=10448
- Falk Firebeard --> Littlefinger
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=10549

LordMaximStark

CREDITS:
Thanks to NPC Editor, Apachii Hair, Jarls New Clothes creators
